He has been having persitant coug and cold and at night he couldn't sleep properly because of cold. After trying out various medications like nebulization and steaming nothing seems to work. The cold seems to go away but starts again during the night especially in cold season. So I was referred to this dr through my neighbour and she immediately suggested seeing an ENT specialist for this as his problem is only in the nose and not lungs. She said we can give temporary medicines which will solve the issue temporally but the real solution is with ENT specialist who can address it more clearly. For us luckily we went to Caveliar hospital Dr.Srinivasa and he gave the right medicine and now my son is completely fine.he asked to come after a month for review. Now my son's cold has come down.

So I strongly recommend the above dr. She is not only friendly but gives good guidance.
